egin="00:35.393" end="00:35.470">ら</span><span begin="00:35.470" end="00:35.896">成</span><span begin="00:35.896" end="00:36.496">長</span><span begin="00:36.496" end="00:36.958">し</span><span begin="00:36.958" end="00:37.647">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">渐渐开始成长</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sokkara seichou shite</span></p><p begin="00:37.989" end="00:41.719" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:37.989" end="00:38.343">ちょ</span><span begin="00:38.343" end="00:38.465">っ</span><span begin="00:38.465" end="00:38.812">ぴ</span><span begin="00:38.812" end="00:38.884">り</span><span begin="00:38.884" end="00:39.097">オ</span><span begin="00:39.097" end="00:39.303">ト</span><span begin="00:39.303" end="00:39.527">ナ</span><span begin="00:39.527" end="00:39.941">に</span><span begin="00:39.941" end="00:40.211">な</span><span begin="00:40.211" end="00:40.365">っ</span><span begin="00:40.365" end="00:40.780">た</span><span begin="00:40.780" end="00:41.191">け</span><span begin="00:41.191" end="00:41.719">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">稍微像个小小的大人</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Choppiri otona ni natta kedo</span></p><p begin="00:42.048" end="00:47.988" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:42.048" end="00:42.247">変</span><span begin="00:42.247" end="00:42.481">わ</span><span begin="00:42.481" end="00:42.679">ら</span><span begin="00:42.679" end="00:42.869">ず</span><span begin="00:42.869" end="00:43.527">に</span> <span begin="00:43.724" end="00:44.118">楽</span><span begin="00:44.118" end="00:44.309">し</span><span begin="00:44.309" end="00:44.537">い</span><span begin="00:44.537" end="00:45.126">を</span> <span begin="00:45.435" end="00:45.635">追</span><span begin="00:45.635" end="00:45.851">い</span><span begin="00:45.851" end="00:46.049">か</span><span begin="00:46.049" end="00:46.249">け</span><span begin="00:46.249" end="00:46.690">て</span><span begin="00:46.690" end="00:47.098">い</span><span begin="00:47.098" end="00:47.536">る</span><span begin="00:47.536" end="00:47.988">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">还是一如既往地追寻那份快乐</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kawarazu ni tanoshii o oikakete iru yo</span></p><p begin="00:48.114" end="00:50.865" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:48.114" end="00:48.168">「</span><span begin="00:48.168" end="00:48.410">名</span><span begin="00:48.410" end="00:48.649">前</span><span begin="00:48.812" end="00:49.235">教</span><span begin="00:49.235" end="00:49.450">え</span><span begin="00:49.450" end="00:49.621">て</span><span begin="00:49.621" end="00:50.658">よ</span><span begin="00:50.658" end="00:50.865">！」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「你叫什么名字呀？」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">"Namae oshiete yo!"</span></p><p begin="00:50.229" end="00:54.335" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:50.229" end="00:50.492">そ</span><span begin="00:50.492" end="00:50.893">の</span><span begin="00:50.893" end="00:51.359">声</span><span begin="00:51.359" end="00:51.547">が</span> <span begin="00:51.547" end="00:51.679">い</span><span begin="00:51.679" end="00:51.792">つ</span><span begin="00:51.792" end="00:52.054">も</span> <span begin="00:52.198" end="00:52.396">い</span><span begin="00:52.396" end="00:52.610">つ</span><span begin="00:52.610" end="00:52.821">ま</span><span begin="00:52.821" end="00:53.016">で</span><span begin="00:53.016" end="00:54.335">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那声呼唤 无论何时都</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono koe ga itsumo itsumademo</span></p><p begin="00:53.652" end="00:54.886" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:53.652" end="00:54.074">響</span><span begin="00:54.074" end="00:54.299">い</span><span begin="00:54.299" end="00:54.511">て</span><span begin="00:54.511" end="00:54.886">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在耳畔回响</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hibiiteru</span></p><p begin="00:54.886" end="00:56.230" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="