>ano kouen o</span></p><p begin="01:15.866" end="01:19.032" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:15.866" end="01:16.269">思</span><span begin="01:16.269" end="01:16.481">い</span><span begin="01:16.481" end="01:16.683">出</span><span begin="01:16.683" end="01:16.911">す</span><span begin="01:16.911" end="01:17.360">よ</span> <span begin="01:17.534" end="01:17.968">思</span><span begin="01:17.968" end="01:18.170">い</span><span begin="01:18.170" end="01:18.358">出</span><span begin="01:18.358" end="01:18.603">す</span><span begin="01:18.603" end="01:19.032">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会想起来的 我会想起来的</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Omoidasu yo omoidasu yo</span></p><p begin="01:19.234" end="01:22.701" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:19.234" end="01:19.441">ト</span><span begin="01:19.441" end="01:19.650">モ</span><span begin="01:19.650" end="01:19.866">ダ</span><span begin="01:19.866" end="01:20.074">チ</span><span begin="01:20.074" end="01:20.711">に</span><span begin="01:20.711" end="01:20.892">な</span><span begin="01:20.892" end="01:21.348">れ</span><span begin="01:21.348" end="01:21.537">る</span><span begin="01:21.537" end="01:21.746">場</span><span begin="01:21.746" end="01:22.701">所</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那个让我们成为朋友的地方</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">tomodachi ni nareru basho</span></p><p begin="01:23.241" end="01:26.435" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:23.241" end="01:23.673">誰</span><span begin="01:23.673" end="01:24.044">も</span><span begin="01:24.044" end="01:24.507">ひ</span><span begin="01:24.507" end="01:24.935">と</span><span begin="01:24.935" end="01:25.143">り</span><span begin="01:25.143" end="01:25.571">じゃ</span><span begin="01:25.571" end="01:25.773">な</span><span begin="01:25.773" end="01:25.965">か</span><span begin="01:25.965" end="01:26.196">っ</span><span begin="01:26.196" end="01:26.435">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">从来没有谁是孤身一人</span><span tt