">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">预言书上 大家一起写下</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yogen no sho ni itsuka naru you ni</span></p><p begin="01:57.905" end="01:59.157" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="01:57.905" end="01:58.106">み</span><span begin="01:58.106" end="01:58.526">ん</span><span begin="01:58.526" end="01:58.748">な</span><span begin="01:58.748" end="01:59.157">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">想要实现的愿望</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Minna de</span></p><p begin="01:59.579" end="02:04.928" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="01:59.579" end="02:00.008">ら</span><span begin="02:00.008" end="02:00.195">く</span><span begin="02:00.195" end="02:00.417">が</span><span begin="02:00.417" end="02:00.617">き</span><span begin="02:00.617" end="02:01.258">帳</span><span begin="02:01.258" end="02:01.698">の</span><span begin="02:01.698" end="02:02.533">上</span><span begin="02:02.533" end="02:02.770">に</span> <span begin="02:03.129" end="02:03.380">好</span><span begin="02:03.380" end="02:03.590">き</span><span begin="02:03.590" end="02:04.019">勝</span><span begin="02:04.019" end="02:04.928">手</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在涂鸦本上随心所欲吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">rakugakichou no ue ni suki katte</span></p><p begin="02:04.654" end="02:05.849" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="02:04.654" end="02:05.068">大</span><span begin="02:05.068" end="02:05.468">丈</span><span begin="02:05.468" end="02:05.849">夫</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没关系的</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Daijoubu</span></p><p begin="02:05.849" end="02:08.703" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="02:05.849" end="02:06.129">少</span><span begin="02:06.129" end="02:06.427">し</span><span begin="02:06.560" end="02:06.757">ケ</span><span begin="02:06.757" end="02:06.927">ガ</span><span begin="02:06.927" end="02:07.191">し</span><span begin="02:07.191" end="02:07.401">て</span><span begin="02:07.401" end="02:08.